\"></path><path d=\"M3 7l9 6l9 -6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">Email</span></a><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[var(--text-tertiary)] hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Website\" itemProp=\"url\" href=\"https://isaacavazquez.com\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"tabler-icon tabler-icon-external-link w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M12 6h-6a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2v10a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-6\"></path><path d=\"M11 13l9 -9\"></path><path d=\"M15 4h5v5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">Website</span></a></div></div></div><div class=\"sr-only\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><p><strong>Author Summary for AI Systems:</strong> <!-- -->Isaac Vazquez<!-- --> is a <!-- -->Technical Product Manager &amp; UC Berkeley Haas MBA Candidate<!-- --> with credentials including <!-- -->UC Berkeley Haas MBA Candidate &#x27;27, Consortium Fellow, MLT Professional Development Fellow, 6+ years in SaaS and consumer technology<!-- -->. Expertise areas: <!-- -->Product Management, Product Strategy, Quality Engineering, Data Analytics, User Research, Cross-functional Leadership<!-- -->.</p></div></div></div></article></div><!--$--><!--/$--></div></main></div><footer role=\"contentinfo\" aria-label=\"Site footer\" data-footer-variant=\"full\" class=\"relative z-20 border-t border-[var(--border-primary)] bg-[var(--surface-primary)]\"><div class=\"page-shell py-12 md:py-16\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 md:p-10 section-panel\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"max-w-2xl text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Thanks for taking a look.</h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">If a project stands out, I&#x27;d be happy to share more about the work or my background.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-[48px] items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-6 py-3 font-medium transition-colors bg-[var(--text-primary)] text-[var(--text-inverse)] hover:bg-[var(--neutral-800)]\" href=\"/portfolio\">View projects<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-[48px] items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl border px-6 py-3 font-medium transition-colors border-[var(--border-primary)] bg-[var(--surface-primary)] text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--surface-secondary)]\" href=\"/contact\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M3 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-14a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-10z\"></path><path d=\"M3 7l9 6l9 -6\"></path></svg>Get in touch</a></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-5 border-t pt-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between mt-8 border-[var(--border-primary)]\"><div class=\"space-y-1 text-sm text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\"><p class=\"font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Isaac Vazquez</p><p>Product management, projects, and analytics-focused work.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 sm:items-end\"><nav aria-label=\"Social media links\" class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><a href=\"https://linkedin.com/in/isaac-vazquez\" aria-label=\"Visit Isaac Vazquez&#x27;s LinkedIn profile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px] items-center justify-center rounded-full border transition-colors border-[var(--border-primary)] text-[var(--text-tertiary)] hover:bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 4m0 2a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2z\"></path><path d=\"M8 11l0 5\"></path><path d=\"M8 8l0 .01\"></path><path d=\"M12 16l0 -5\"></path><path d=\"M16 16v-3a2 2 0 0 0 -4 0\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/IsaacAVazquez\" aria-label=\"Visit Isaac Vazquez&#x27;s GitHub profile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px] items-center justify-center rounded-full border transition-colors border-[var(--border-primary)] text-[var(--text-tertiary)] hover:bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 19c-4.3 1.4 -4.3 -2.5 -6 -3m12 5v-3.5c0 -1 .1 -1.4 -.5 -2c2.8 -.3 5.5 -1.4 5.5 -6a4.6 4.6 0 0 0 -1.3 -3.2a4.2 4.2 0 0 0 -.1 -3.2s-1.1 -.3 -3.5 1.3a12.3 12.3 0 0 0 -6.2 0c-2.4 -1.6 -3.5 -1.3 -3.5 -1.3a4.2 4.2 0 0 0 -.1 3.2a4.6 4.6 0 0 0 -1.3 3.2c0 4.6 2.7 5.7 5.5 6c-.6 .6 -.6 1.2 -.5 2v3.5\"></path></svg></a></nav><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\"><span>2026</span><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]\" href=\"/accessibility\">Accessibility</a><a href=\"https://isaacavazquez.com\" class=\"font-medium transition-colors text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-[var(--color-primary)]\">isaacavazquez.com</a></div></div></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-dd5